title: Joy Ride / Joy Ride 2  Drive-In Double Feature
description:
Drive-In Double Fature #13

#1
Joy Ride                                                              <a href=" http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0206314/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.imdb.com/title/tt0206314/</a>

Three young people take a rod trip. When the carless of the brothers talks the other into commiting a prank. But 
he turns out to be a psychotic truck driver bent on revenge.

#2
Joy Ride 2                                                            <a href=" http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1140941/" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW"> http://www.imdb.com/title/tt1140941/</a>

Rusty is back and even more psychotic than in the first one. There is a "game" scene, you will know it when you 
see it that is very well played up. Obviously rusty has been doing this a while.
